p.s:
The full reading on the caliper, in centimeter, is given by
            \begin{align*}2.7 + 0.09 
              = 2.79centimeter.\end{align*}

The length corresponding to one mark on the rotating scale
            is given by
            \begin{align*}\frac{0.5millimeter}
              {50} = 0.01millimeter.\end{align*}
